1
00:01:31,180 --> 00:01:35,750
(Destiny and Saving)

2
00:01:35,780 --> 00:01:38,759
(Episode 6)

3
00:01:44,910 --> 00:01:46,060
There is no fire to boil the water.

4
00:01:46,090 --> 00:01:47,580
We'll have to make do with some cold water for now.

5
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,830
You usually boil

6
00:01:51,140 --> 00:01:52,820
your water before drinking it?

7
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,229
Yeah.

8
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,890
From now on,

9
00:01:55,979 --> 00:01:57,960
you should start getting used to drinking hot water too.

10
00:01:58,539 --> 00:02:00,190
Since I've decided to be with you,

11
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,640
naturally I should also learn your ways.

12
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,370
Is it because of the strange cold condition you have

13
00:02:11,390 --> 00:02:13,330
that you live alone in the snow plains of Mang Mountain?

14
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,650
Yes and no.

15
00:02:16,820 --> 00:02:18,950
My master had me live in the snow plains

16
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:21,840
so that my condition

17
00:02:21,940 --> 00:02:23,900
would harm me less.

18
00:02:24,190 --> 00:02:25,240
Besides,

19
00:02:25,270 --> 00:02:28,110
I can't control the cold energy within my body.

20
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:30,680
If I lived with others,

21
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,440
I'd end up hurting them.

22
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,600
However...

23
00:02:35,070 --> 00:02:36,050
you're different.

24
00:02:37,910 --> 00:02:40,300
You're not afraid of my cold condition,

25
00:02:40,540 --> 00:02:43,510
and when my cold energy erupts,

26
00:02:43,670 --> 00:02:44,870
you can even help to dispel it from me.

27
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:46,280
Therefore,

28
00:02:46,329 --> 00:02:48,540
I can live with you.

29
00:02:51,460 --> 00:02:52,510
I've only...

30
00:02:52,550 --> 00:02:55,060
temporarily stabilized your heart meridian with my inner energy.

31
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:56,610
I didn't cure you completely.

32
00:02:56,910 --> 00:02:57,740
I think

33
00:02:57,770 --> 00:02:59,329
anyone with some cultivation

34
00:02:59,350 --> 00:03:00,450
could do that.

35
00:03:00,860 --> 00:03:01,730
That's not right.

36
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,600
My master couldn't do it.

37
00:03:05,650 --> 00:03:08,050
Your cold condition forces you to live in seclusion.

38
00:03:08,890 --> 00:03:10,050
This place has green mountains and clear waters

39
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:11,620
and is peaceful and undisturbed.

40
00:03:11,890 --> 00:03:12,910
It's indeed a good place to live.

41
00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:15,630
I'll listen to you.

42
00:03:18,010 --> 00:03:19,610
(Return to Shushan Sect quickly)

43
00:03:21,300 --> 00:03:22,370
I should go back to attend my midday lessons now.

44
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,420
Can't you skip the midday lessons today?

45
00:03:24,450 --> 00:03:26,110
No one should miss the six daily lessons at three different times.

46
00:03:26,130 --> 00:03:27,260
That's Master's rule.

47
00:03:27,450 --> 00:03:29,800
But your master isn't here.

48
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:31,000
What are you afraid of?

49
00:03:31,420 --> 00:03:33,440
It's the same whether he's here or not.

50
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:36,050
Such a goody-goody.

51
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,380
Such a goody-goody.

52
00:03:39,470 --> 00:03:40,440
So obedient.

53
00:03:43,870 --> 00:03:44,870
Then let me ask you,

54
00:03:45,010 --> 00:03:46,829
if you broke the rules,

55
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:48,550
would your master severely punish you?

56
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:52,400
If you won't be punished, what are you afraid of?

57
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:55,370
He wouldn't punish you, so what are you afraid of?

58
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,120
It's not that there's no punishment.

59
00:03:58,180 --> 00:04:00,800
It's that I've... never done anything wrong.

60
00:04:07,050 --> 00:04:08,890
(Goddess Temple)

61
00:04:08,890 --> 00:04:10,690
What is it about?
(Goddess Temple)

62
00:04:10,690 --> 00:04:11,080
(Goddess Temple)

63
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:11,800
It's so late.
(Goddess Temple)

64
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:11,830
(Goddess Temple)

65
00:04:11,830 --> 00:04:13,800
Can't it wait until tomorrow?
(Goddess Temple)

66
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,230
I want to teach you the Ice Sword Technique.

67
00:04:19,540 --> 00:04:21,380
It can help suppress the cold energy in your body.

68
00:04:21,649 --> 00:04:22,790
Start practicing from now on,

69
00:04:22,910 --> 00:04:24,330
and once you've mastered it,

70
00:04:24,380 --> 00:04:26,290
you can go down the mountain and live peacefully among people.

71
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,670
Go down the mountain?

72
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:29,740
But I never thought about leaving the mountain.

73
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:32,370
I think it's quite peaceful and nice here,

74
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:33,640
just like Mang Mountain.

75
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,320
You're teaching me swordsmanship

76
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,520
just so you can leave me, right?

77
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:02,790
You still won't take me with you, will you?

78
00:05:04,060 --> 00:05:05,640
You and I are destined for different paths.

79
00:05:06,460 --> 00:05:08,180
You will have to live on your own eventually.

80
00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:10,320
But I promise you,

81
00:05:10,430 --> 00:05:11,580
I will do everything in my power

82
00:05:11,610 --> 00:05:12,750
to cure your cold condition.

83
00:05:13,590 --> 00:05:14,240
I'm tired.

84
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:14,770
I'm done practicing.

85
00:06:06,910 --> 00:06:08,030
Do you know

86
00:06:08,050 --> 00:06:11,210
why your consciousness has drifted here?

87
00:06:11,230 --> 00:06:13,560
For the past ten years, I have never neglected my cultivation, day or night.

88
00:06:15,220 --> 00:06:16,420
My mind has never wandered.

89
00:06:16,450 --> 00:06:18,220
I don't know why I'm so absent-minded at this moment.

90
00:06:18,250 --> 00:06:21,090
There's an unresolved demonic obstacle in your heart.

91
00:06:21,270 --> 00:06:22,460
For the past decade,

92
00:06:22,550 --> 00:06:26,250
you've only been forcibly burying it deep within your consciousness.

93
00:06:26,390 --> 00:06:28,160
But the moment your guard is down,

94
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:30,580
it will seize the opportunity to resurface.

95
00:06:30,590 --> 00:06:31,550
A demonic obstacle in my heart?

96
00:06:32,790 --> 00:06:33,950
I've been cultivating with a clear mind,

97
00:06:33,990 --> 00:06:34,990
believing that my heart and spirit are unified.

98
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,790
I don't have distracting thoughts or demonic obstacles in my heart.

99
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:39,230
This is not something I can answer for you.

100
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:41,290
Ask your own heart.

101
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:47,400
Mo Xiao...

102
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:51,960
Even if I am reborn as a ghost,

103
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,970
-Lixue!
-I will come back...

104
00:06:54,820 --> 00:06:56,890
to take revenge on you all!

105
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:59,470
Mo Xiao, you really did it.

106
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:00,360
Don't be afraid.

107
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:01,040
Hold me tight.

108
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,240
I can protect you.

109
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:11,530
My Lord, nothing escapes your eyes.

110
00:07:11,550 --> 00:07:13,110
I indeed have a karmic burden

111
00:07:13,130 --> 00:07:14,470
buried deep in my heart for 10 years.

112
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,150
Ten years ago...

113
00:07:16,890 --> 00:07:18,890
because of a single careless moment, I caused Lixue's death,

114
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:21,520
making her... fall off a cliff.

115
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:23,260
Since that day, her death has become

116
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,360
a karmic burden in my heart

117
00:07:24,380 --> 00:07:25,380
that I cannot overcome.

118
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,180
If I could live this life over again,

119
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:31,140
I swear I'd never let such a thing happen again.

120
00:07:31,980 --> 00:07:33,810
If you don't face the tribulations in your fate,

121
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:35,900
you can't overcome your karmic obstacles.

122
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:38,000
Everything is predetermined by fate.

123
00:07:38,070 --> 00:07:40,550
You must walk your path wisely.

124
00:07:40,570 --> 00:07:41,420
My Lord.

125
00:07:41,620 --> 00:07:42,300
My Lord.

126
00:07:42,620 --> 00:07:43,880
My Lord, please show me the way!

127
00:09:29,530 --> 00:09:30,500
What are you doing?

128
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:34,460
Your lips are so warm.

129
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,410
What's wrong?

130
00:09:38,910 --> 00:09:40,160
Are you feeling hot?

131
00:09:40,430 --> 00:09:42,070
Your face is so red.

132
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:44,100
If you're overheated,

133
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,890
you can go over there and wash up.

134
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,090
The water there is cool.

135
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:52,440
Do you want to play in the water with me?

136
00:09:52,460 --> 00:09:53,170
Stop talking.

137
00:09:53,550 --> 00:09:54,590
Hurry and put your clothes on.

138
00:10:05,800 --> 00:10:06,430
Lixue?

139
00:10:08,450 --> 00:10:09,490
Lixue?

140
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,230
Where did you get that phoenix-shaped mark

141
00:10:12,250 --> 00:10:13,010
on the back of your neck?

142
00:10:14,290 --> 00:10:15,900
You mean this?

143
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,280
This

144
00:10:17,300 --> 00:10:19,680
is a birthmark that I've had since I was born.

145
00:10:20,190 --> 00:10:21,450
My father told me

146
00:10:21,470 --> 00:10:24,110
that it's my unique mark in the world.

147
00:10:25,270 --> 00:10:27,290
If you can't find me in the future,

148
00:10:27,310 --> 00:10:28,890
you can find me through this.

149
00:10:29,740 --> 00:10:31,010
What is this?

150
00:10:31,350 --> 00:10:32,600
This is my birthmark.

151
00:10:32,650 --> 00:10:35,090
My father said it's unique in the world.

152
00:10:35,180 --> 00:10:36,200
If I ever get lost,

153
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:38,370
you can find me by this mark.

154
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,000
Lixue...

155
00:10:50,810 --> 00:10:52,010
You are Lixue, right?

156
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:54,950
Lixue?

157
00:10:55,310 --> 00:10:56,690
Who is Lixue?

158
00:11:02,070 --> 00:11:03,620
(Goddess Temple)

159
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:09,000
Who are you really?

160
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,400
Are you really Lixue?

161
00:11:12,890 --> 00:11:14,740
Then why don't you remember anything about the past?

162
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:16,710
Or...

163
00:11:17,750 --> 00:11:19,560
is all this just a coincidence?

164
00:11:21,190 --> 00:11:21,870
Master,

165
00:11:21,940 --> 00:11:22,910
what do you need?

166
00:11:22,940 --> 00:11:23,750
Floren,

167
00:11:23,820 --> 00:11:25,610
have you found any information about the Snow Demon of Mang Mountain?

168
00:11:25,860 --> 00:11:28,310
It was the first time that Snow Demon showed itself and stirred up trouble,

169
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:30,800
so I haven't found any information about its past yet.

170
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:32,780
Then...

171
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,560
what about Wu Chen, the orphan girl from Mang Mountain?

172
00:11:35,050 --> 00:11:36,230
Do you have any information about her?

173
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:37,680
I've traced things back to the time

174
00:11:37,700 --> 00:11:39,580
when I first started collecting intelligence for you, Master.

175
00:11:39,680 --> 00:11:41,320
But all the information I could find showed

176
00:11:41,470 --> 00:11:42,510
that Miss Wu Chen

177
00:11:42,530 --> 00:11:44,050
had indeed been living on Mang Mountain all along.

178
00:11:44,670 --> 00:11:46,590
Who exactly is the "Master" that Miss Wu Chen

179
00:11:46,900 --> 00:11:48,010
speaks of?

180
00:11:48,110 --> 00:11:49,350
I haven't yet detected any signs

181
00:11:49,430 --> 00:11:50,830
of a second person on Mang Mountain.

182
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:54,150
Is it possible that Lixue didn't actually die?

183
00:11:56,570 --> 00:11:57,270
Master,

184
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,020
do you have any other instructions?

185
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,160
That's all.

186
00:12:00,540 --> 00:12:01,860
Continue to investigate the real reason

187
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:03,400
why the Snow Demon of Mang Mountain suddenly appeared and wreaked havoc.

188
00:12:04,030 --> 00:12:04,470
Yes, Master.

189
00:12:17,510 --> 00:12:18,070
Wu Chen?

190
00:12:18,760 --> 00:12:19,690
Why are you here?

191
00:12:20,790 --> 00:12:21,830
Where are you going?

192
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:23,610
I'm here to remind you

193
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:26,160
that I haven't learned the sword technique you taught me yet,

194
00:12:26,530 --> 00:12:27,900
so you can't sneak away.

195
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,280
Is that why

196
00:12:29,300 --> 00:12:31,270
you've been guarding outside my room door?

197
00:12:32,350 --> 00:12:34,500
It may be a dumb method,

198
00:12:34,870 --> 00:12:36,460
but I'm telling you now

199
00:12:36,590 --> 00:12:37,830
that if you sneak away,

200
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,350
I will chase after you,

201
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:42,470
and then, what happened in Mang Mountain Village might happen again.

202
00:12:43,150 --> 00:12:45,670
If my cold energy were to burst out,

203
00:12:45,790 --> 00:12:46,750
it would be terrible.

204
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:52,840
Alright.

205
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:55,020
I'll take you with me tomorrow.

206
00:12:55,350 --> 00:12:56,440
Let's go now?

207
00:12:56,460 --> 00:12:57,550
We'll set out tomorrow.

208
00:12:58,470 --> 00:12:59,030
Back to the Shushan Sect.

209
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:19,920
Mo Xiao,

210
00:13:20,020 --> 00:13:22,190
can this thing really fly?

211
00:13:22,290 --> 00:13:22,910
Get on.

212
00:13:23,980 --> 00:13:25,540
I'll pass.

213
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:27,690
I'm pretty fast on my feet.

214
00:13:30,450 --> 00:13:31,450
Mo Xiao,

215
00:13:31,640 --> 00:13:34,720
this thing used to carry only one person.

216
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:36,240
Now it has to carry two.

217
00:13:36,260 --> 00:13:37,270
Are you sure it's okay?

218
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,520
Besides,

219
00:13:38,540 --> 00:13:41,700
what if I fall off

220
00:13:41,720 --> 00:13:42,560
in mid-air?

221
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,600
Have you thought about that?

222
00:13:44,620 --> 00:13:45,320
Stand firm.

223
00:14:27,540 --> 00:14:28,790
We're stable now.

224
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:30,610
Can you take your hand off me now?

225
00:14:33,530 --> 00:14:34,450
Mo Xiao.

226
00:14:34,830 --> 00:14:36,320
Is that a mountain?

227
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,910
Is that a village down there?

228
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:40,800
It's so small.

229
00:14:43,110 --> 00:14:44,300
Are those clouds?

230
00:14:57,490 --> 00:14:59,150
(Xuanqing Court)

231
00:15:02,940 --> 00:15:04,170
This is Xuanqing Court.

232
00:15:08,490 --> 00:15:09,430
(Xuanqing Court)

233
00:15:09,430 --> 00:15:10,910
Xuanqing Court?
(Xuanqing Court)

234
00:15:11,710 --> 00:15:13,940
I feel like I've been here before.

235
00:15:19,850 --> 00:15:26,330
(Xuanqing Court)

236
00:15:38,110 --> 00:15:39,110
Why...

237
00:15:39,790 --> 00:15:40,990
does it feel so familiar?

238
00:15:53,130 --> 00:15:54,580
This is the Shushan Sect?

239
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:56,800
This is the forbidden area of the Shushan Sect.

240
00:15:57,520 --> 00:15:58,840
It's where my master and I

241
00:15:58,940 --> 00:16:00,440
used to seclude ourselves for cultivation.

242
00:16:00,590 --> 00:16:01,390
Master?

243
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:03,420
So your master is also here?

244
00:16:03,720 --> 00:16:05,520
He passed away when I was 8.

245
00:16:05,920 --> 00:16:07,760
Later, I lived here with my senior and junior disciples.

246
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:09,550
But now, no one lives here anymore.

247
00:16:10,730 --> 00:16:11,920
No one lives here anymore?

248
00:16:12,030 --> 00:16:13,390
Then where do you live now?

249
00:16:14,310 --> 00:16:16,010
I am a disciple of the Luntian Branch of the Shushan Sect.

250
00:16:16,330 --> 00:16:17,650
Naturally, I need to return and report back.

251
00:16:18,640 --> 00:16:20,400
Then I'll go back with you.

252
00:16:21,110 --> 00:16:21,970
Wu Chen,

253
00:16:22,130 --> 00:16:24,490
we don't know when your cold energy will erupt again.

254
00:16:24,860 --> 00:16:26,500
If what happened in Mang Mountain Village were to occur here,

255
00:16:26,530 --> 00:16:28,510
it wouldn't end as well as it did in Mang Mountain Village.

256
00:16:28,970 --> 00:16:30,740
So, it's safer for you to stay here for now.

257
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:32,420
After I return from reporting,

258
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:34,620
I'll cure your cold condition and then send you down the mountain.

259
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:37,170
I've known you for so long,

260
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:39,180
and the thing you say most often

261
00:16:39,210 --> 00:16:40,600
is that you want to send me away.

262
00:16:41,470 --> 00:16:43,130
I've already told you.

263
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:44,970
You're different from others.

264
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:46,990
I won't leave you.

265
00:16:48,310 --> 00:16:48,880
Wu Chen,

266
00:16:49,620 --> 00:16:51,020
I've brought you back to the Shushan Sect

267
00:16:51,040 --> 00:16:52,440
to prevent your cold energy from erupting again

268
00:16:52,910 --> 00:16:54,460
and harming innocent people.

269
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:56,990
But the rules here are strict.

270
00:16:57,140 --> 00:16:58,740
Non-disciples are not allowed to enter.

271
00:16:59,380 --> 00:17:00,350
With no other choice,

272
00:17:01,030 --> 00:17:03,170
I brought you to the forbidden area behind the mountain.

273
00:17:03,530 --> 00:17:04,180
Don't worry.

274
00:17:04,369 --> 00:17:05,560
There's a barrier here.

275
00:17:05,670 --> 00:17:07,520
No one, except for me, can enter without permission.

276
00:17:07,660 --> 00:17:08,740
You'll be safe as long as you stay here.

277
00:17:09,569 --> 00:17:10,650
But remember,

