552
00:28:18,350 --> 00:28:19,830
Can't I improve my diet

553
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:21,190
and try something new?

554
00:28:29,080 --> 00:28:30,770
Here, the disciple of the Shushan Sect, Mo Xiao,

555
00:28:30,950 --> 00:28:33,660
sincerely asks the aid of you, Divine Healer, to save a lonely orphan girl.

556
00:28:33,850 --> 00:28:35,340
This girl's condition is peculiar.

557
00:28:35,550 --> 00:28:37,140
There's a strange cold energy within her body.

558
00:28:37,390 --> 00:28:38,560
The cold energy within her is overwhelming,

559
00:28:38,830 --> 00:28:40,350
and ordinary humans cannot approach her.

560
00:28:40,950 --> 00:28:42,660
When frightened or angered,

561
00:28:42,790 --> 00:28:44,170
frost gathers on her brow,

562
00:28:44,330 --> 00:28:45,360
and her face turns pale.

563
00:28:45,930 --> 00:28:46,970
In her presence,

564
00:28:47,090 --> 00:28:48,210
frost spreads within a hundred paces,

565
00:28:48,560 --> 00:28:49,860
freezing everything in its path.

566
00:29:20,950 --> 00:29:21,690
(Spirit Soaring Through the Skies)

567
00:29:23,400 --> 00:29:25,900
(Spirit Soaring Through the Skies)

568
00:29:27,030 --> 00:29:28,330
If I don't get the swordsmanship right...

569
00:29:28,470 --> 00:29:29,790
it must be your fault.

570
00:29:38,760 --> 00:29:39,890
Wait for me!

571
00:29:45,230 --> 00:29:48,160
I wonder how Snowy is doing now.

572
00:30:02,400 --> 00:30:04,150
(Spirit Soaring Through the Skies)

573
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:31,160
What took you so long?

574
00:30:33,070 --> 00:30:34,360
Something held me up.

575
00:30:35,290 --> 00:30:35,950
Oh, right.

576
00:30:36,950 --> 00:30:38,550
I bought you some glutinous rice balls.

577
00:30:50,470 --> 00:30:51,430
Little birds?

578
00:30:52,760 --> 00:30:54,250
These are two spirit birds I've raised,

579
00:30:54,470 --> 00:30:55,790
Blackie and Whitey.

580
00:30:55,950 --> 00:30:57,800
I brought them here because I thought you might feel lonely

581
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:59,400
staying in this courtyard alone.

582
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:08,200
They don't shy away from you?

583
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,800
Do they usually shy away from people's touch?

584
00:31:11,360 --> 00:31:12,280
Besides me,

585
00:31:12,350 --> 00:31:13,640
no one has ever touched them.

586
00:31:14,960 --> 00:31:15,850
Looks like...

587
00:31:16,950 --> 00:31:17,950
you have a special connection with them.

588
00:31:19,230 --> 00:31:20,470
Of course,

589
00:31:20,830 --> 00:31:22,760
I'm not like the others.

590
00:31:24,910 --> 00:31:26,480
Quick, give me your hand!

591
00:31:31,110 --> 00:31:32,870
Could it be that they still remember you?

592
00:31:39,920 --> 00:31:40,620
What's wrong?

593
00:31:41,100 --> 00:31:42,060
Don't you like them?

594
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:45,000
It's not that I don't like birds.

595
00:31:45,230 --> 00:31:47,110
They just remind me of my Snowy.

596
00:31:47,920 --> 00:31:49,610
I've left Mang Mountain,

597
00:31:49,950 --> 00:31:51,610
but Snowy is still there.

598
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:54,470
I don't know if she'll be able to find

599
00:31:54,720 --> 00:31:56,920
any wild berries to eat on her own.

600
00:31:57,710 --> 00:31:58,870
If you're worried,

601
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:01,130
I can make time to go back to Mang Mountain

602
00:32:01,190 --> 00:32:02,390
and bring Snowy here.

603
00:32:02,880 --> 00:32:03,520
Really?

604
00:32:07,010 --> 00:32:07,940
It's getting late.

605
00:32:08,110 --> 00:32:08,880
I should head back now.

606
00:32:10,490 --> 00:32:11,920
Leaving so soon?

607
00:32:20,520 --> 00:32:21,330
Oh, right.

608
00:32:24,030 --> 00:32:24,950
This is the Mind Stone.

609
00:32:25,490 --> 00:32:26,520
Keep it with you.

610
00:32:27,230 --> 00:32:28,030
If anything happens,

611
00:32:28,070 --> 00:32:29,330
you can use it to summon me.

612
00:32:29,710 --> 00:32:30,640
I'll come right away.

613
00:32:35,490 --> 00:32:36,440
Rest early.

614
00:33:23,760 --> 00:33:24,420
Mo Xiao.

615
00:33:25,230 --> 00:33:26,150
What is it?

616
00:33:28,790 --> 00:33:30,350
I didn't expect this to actually work!

617
00:33:32,630 --> 00:33:33,510
No need to test it again.

618
00:33:34,030 --> 00:33:35,950
Call me when you really need me.

619
00:33:53,580 --> 00:33:54,500
What is it now?

620
00:33:55,470 --> 00:33:58,580
Why won't they let me hold them while I sleep?

621
00:34:00,280 --> 00:34:01,400
You want to hold them while you sleep?

622
00:34:02,980 --> 00:34:05,470
When I was on Mang Mountain,

623
00:34:05,680 --> 00:34:08,010
I always slept while holding Snowy.

624
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:12,449
These two aren't like Snowy.

625
00:34:12,840 --> 00:34:14,250
They can't cuddle with you on the bed.

626
00:34:29,630 --> 00:34:30,520
Go to sleep now.

627
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:34,199
Can you wait until I fall asleep before you leave?

628
00:34:48,080 --> 00:34:48,920
Yesterday,

629
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:51,710
I received a letter from the head of the Tianyu Sect,

630
00:34:52,570 --> 00:34:55,989
inviting Mo Xiao to attend a discourse on the Dao.

631
00:34:56,590 --> 00:34:58,510
It must be because of our Shushan Sect's Young Sect Leader's

632
00:34:58,590 --> 00:34:59,750
recent demon-slaying journey

633
00:35:00,080 --> 00:35:02,520
that has spread his name far and wide.

634
00:35:02,640 --> 00:35:03,730
This is a great opportunity

635
00:35:03,800 --> 00:35:05,080
to showcase

636
00:35:05,160 --> 00:35:07,360
the style and grace of our Shushan's sword immortals.

637
00:35:07,560 --> 00:35:08,280
That's right.

638
00:35:08,710 --> 00:35:09,520
Mo Xiao.

639
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:12,710
Yes, Master.

640
00:35:12,750 --> 00:35:15,310
Since this is an invitation from the head of the Tianyu Sect,

641
00:35:15,550 --> 00:35:17,390
you should depart immediately.

642
00:35:18,080 --> 00:35:20,300
They are holding a recruitment event,

643
00:35:20,430 --> 00:35:22,770
which will be a good opportunity for you to gain some experience.

644
00:35:23,520 --> 00:35:23,950
Yes, Master.

645
00:35:24,390 --> 00:35:25,950
Come on, come on, quickly, sit back.

646
00:35:30,600 --> 00:35:31,310
Me...

647
00:35:33,230 --> 00:35:33,910
Lingyun,

648
00:35:34,640 --> 00:35:36,080
do you have something to say?

649
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:38,880
Sect Leader,

650
00:35:39,270 --> 00:35:40,050
I have nothing to say.

651
00:35:40,200 --> 00:35:42,200
Well, if there's nothing else,

652
00:35:42,630 --> 00:35:43,430
everyone, dismissed.

653
00:35:43,880 --> 00:35:44,360
Okay.

654
00:35:50,880 --> 00:35:51,290
Zisu!

655
00:35:51,290 --> 00:35:51,360
(Virtuous Radiance)
Zisu!

656
00:35:51,360 --> 00:35:52,350
(Virtuous Radiance)

657
00:35:52,350 --> 00:35:53,380
Where is your Young Sect Leader?
(Virtuous Radiance)

658
00:35:53,380 --> 00:35:54,020
(Virtuous Radiance)

659
00:35:58,870 --> 00:35:59,830
You rude girl,

660
00:35:59,850 --> 00:36:02,130
can you change this bad habit of ignoring people?

661
00:36:02,310 --> 00:36:04,230
Be careful, or you might not be able to get married in the future.

662
00:36:04,470 --> 00:36:05,520
Who says I want to get married?

663
00:36:06,170 --> 00:36:07,010
What?

664
00:36:07,190 --> 00:36:08,280
You don't want to get married?

665
00:36:08,390 --> 00:36:10,710
Don't tell me you're going to stay with your Young Sect Leader for life.

666
00:36:10,870 --> 00:36:11,430
That's right.

667
00:36:11,800 --> 00:36:13,950
I'll make glutinous rice balls for the Young Sect Leader for life.

668
00:36:14,040 --> 00:36:15,210
Glutinous rice balls?

669
00:36:15,450 --> 00:36:16,990
This guy wants to eat glutinous rice balls again?

670
00:36:17,110 --> 00:36:17,830
Yes.

671
00:36:17,920 --> 00:36:19,360
For the first time in his life,

672
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:21,020
he's craved something like this.

673
00:36:21,080 --> 00:36:22,200
Before he left on the long journey this time,

674
00:36:22,230 --> 00:36:23,620
he especially asked me to make more.

675
00:36:23,680 --> 00:36:25,400
I guess he wants to take them to eat on the road.

676
00:36:25,470 --> 00:36:26,230
He already left?

677
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:27,950
When?

678
00:36:29,190 --> 00:36:29,710
Just now.

679
00:36:31,080 --> 00:36:31,980
Oh no.

680
00:36:50,020 --> 00:36:50,890
Come out.

681
00:36:56,590 --> 00:36:58,230
Since I've followed you all the way here,

682
00:36:58,310 --> 00:36:59,590
there's no need for you to hide anything anymore.

683
00:37:00,120 --> 00:37:02,460
You little rascal, are you hiding a beauty in here?

684
00:37:02,630 --> 00:37:04,540
I'd like to see what kind of beauty

685
00:37:04,670 --> 00:37:06,430
likes to eat these glutinous rice balls.

686
00:37:06,550 --> 00:37:07,870
It's not what you think.

687
00:37:09,110 --> 00:37:10,550
You're quite good at hiding people, aren't you?

688
00:37:10,670 --> 00:37:11,670
Hiding her in this place.

689
00:37:11,760 --> 00:37:13,320
Sect Leader definitely won't find out.

690
00:37:13,520 --> 00:37:14,740
It's not that I'm good at hiding people.

691
00:37:14,760 --> 00:37:16,090
I just don't want to cause trouble.

692
00:37:24,150 --> 00:37:25,190
Who are you?

693
00:37:25,630 --> 00:37:26,440
Wu Chen.

694
00:37:26,800 --> 00:37:27,520
This is...

695
00:37:27,640 --> 00:37:29,440
So, this is the woman you brought back?

696
00:37:29,830 --> 00:37:31,710
I don't see anything special about her appearance.

697
00:37:32,150 --> 00:37:33,630
What does "appearance" mean?

698
00:37:34,040 --> 00:37:35,520
Are you a bit slow in the head?

699
00:37:35,600 --> 00:37:37,250
What does that mean?

700
00:37:37,790 --> 00:37:39,570
Do you think I'm stupid,

701
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:40,880
or is she really stupid?

702
00:37:41,150 --> 00:37:42,410
She thinks you're stupid.

703
00:37:42,910 --> 00:37:43,520
Alright.

704
00:37:43,540 --> 00:37:44,280
Miss Wu Chen

705
00:37:44,300 --> 00:37:45,580
grew up in the snow plains of Mang Mountain.

706
00:37:45,610 --> 00:37:46,580
She's unfamiliar with the ways of the world.

707
00:37:47,120 --> 00:37:47,800
Don't mess around.

708
00:37:48,280 --> 00:37:49,650
Your name is Wu Chen, right?

709
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,390
Then, let me introduce myself too.

710
00:37:52,160 --> 00:37:52,950
I am

711
00:37:53,120 --> 00:37:54,800
handsome beyond compare, graceful as a jade orchid,

712
00:37:54,820 --> 00:37:57,040
and the unparalleled Young Master of the Tielyv Branch of the Shushan Sect,

713
00:37:57,100 --> 00:37:58,290
Xie Lingyun.

714
00:38:00,260 --> 00:38:02,650
Why is his name so long?

715
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:03,920
Because he's stupid.

716
00:38:04,910 --> 00:38:06,430
His name is Xie Lingyun.

717
00:38:06,630 --> 00:38:08,110
Xie Lingyun?

718
00:38:09,790 --> 00:38:11,860
You're the one who gave us those gold leaves.

719
00:38:12,510 --> 00:38:14,320
And they were all spent by you, right?

720
00:38:14,360 --> 00:38:16,000
I exchanged them for things.

721
00:38:16,190 --> 00:38:16,710
Exchange?

722
00:38:16,930 --> 00:38:18,110
That's called "buying."

723
00:38:18,390 --> 00:38:19,150
What did you buy?

724
00:38:20,220 --> 00:38:23,110
I exchanged them for glutinous rice balls,

725
00:38:23,140 --> 00:38:24,250
clothes,

726
00:38:24,470 --> 00:38:25,880
and a pinwheel.

727
00:38:26,160 --> 00:38:28,200
Anyway, those gold leaves were really useful.

728
00:38:28,220 --> 00:38:30,160
Can you bring us more next time?

729
00:38:30,230 --> 00:38:31,000
Next time?

730
00:38:31,030 --> 00:38:32,750
I can't believe you actually said that.

731
00:38:33,470 --> 00:38:35,520
I must say, you two are a perfect match.

732
00:38:35,630 --> 00:38:36,510
Don't talk nonsense.

733
00:38:36,910 --> 00:38:37,770
Come in with me.

734
00:38:37,800 --> 00:38:38,760
I've got serious business to discuss with you.

735
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:40,010
Wu Chen.

736
00:38:40,950 --> 00:38:42,360
Glutinous rice balls?

737
00:38:55,610 --> 00:38:57,680
You want me to take care of Wu Chen?

738
00:38:57,770 --> 00:38:58,930
No, no, no, Mo Xiao.

739
00:38:59,080 --> 00:39:00,200
If her cold condition flares up,

740
00:39:00,230 --> 00:39:01,320
I really can't handle it.

741
00:39:01,340 --> 00:39:02,080
Besides,

742
00:39:02,100 --> 00:39:03,480
if the Sect Leader finds out,

743
00:39:03,560 --> 00:39:04,950
he'll definitely lock me up in the Tielyv Branch,

744
00:39:04,970 --> 00:39:06,600
and my dad would beat me half to death.

745
00:39:06,640 --> 00:39:07,400
Mo Xiao,

746
00:39:07,560 --> 00:39:08,880
we're brothers.

747
00:39:09,150 --> 00:39:10,350
You can't throw me under the bus like this.

748
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:12,670
I've set up a barrier outside Xuanqing Court.

749
00:39:12,790 --> 00:39:14,630
I'll tell you how to open this barrier.

750
00:39:14,800 --> 00:39:15,520
Don't worry.

751
00:39:15,640 --> 00:39:16,760
No one else can get in.

752
00:39:17,680 --> 00:39:19,960
But that's not a solution if it goes on for too long, right?

753
00:39:21,030 --> 00:39:21,870
It won't be for too long.

754
00:39:22,230 --> 00:39:23,840
I'm looking for someone to help treat her cold condition.

755
00:39:24,110 --> 00:39:25,690
Once Wu Chen's cold condition is cured,

756
00:39:25,840 --> 00:39:26,880
I'll send her down the mountain

757
00:39:26,900 --> 00:39:28,390
and let her live a quiet life in some ordinary town.

758
00:39:28,630 --> 00:39:29,390
Who are you looking for?

759
00:39:30,440 --> 00:39:31,620
Speaking of this person,

760
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:32,800
I still need to ask for your help.

761
00:39:32,910 --> 00:39:34,840
Help me find the best peach blossom wine in the world.

762
00:39:35,080 --> 00:39:36,000
Peach blossom wine?

763
00:39:40,760 --> 00:39:42,970
Could the person you're looking for be the Divine Healer, Shi Bujiu?

764
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:43,430
That's right.

765
00:39:45,980 --> 00:39:46,840
Blackie.

766
00:39:55,620 --> 00:39:56,530
Mo Xiao.

767
00:40:03,410 --> 00:40:04,320
Mo Xiao.

768
00:40:04,650 --> 00:40:06,300
Why do you look like you're afraid of her?

769
00:40:06,430 --> 00:40:07,560
You're afraid of me?

770
00:40:09,080 --> 00:40:09,600
Why...

771
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:12,040
why would I be afraid of you?

772
00:40:14,560 --> 00:40:15,760
Look at you,

773
00:40:16,310 --> 00:40:18,150
it's like you're afraid she's gonna eat you alive or something.

774
00:40:28,230 --> 00:40:28,840
Mo Xiao.

775
00:40:29,670 --> 00:40:31,250
You're blushing.

776
00:40:31,510 --> 00:40:33,370
This is the first time in my life that I've seen you blush.

777
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:34,180
Tell me,

778
00:40:34,470 --> 00:40:35,630
are you hiding something from me?

779
00:40:35,650 --> 00:40:36,680
Come clean!

780
00:40:37,560 --> 00:40:38,040
I...

781
00:40:39,470 --> 00:40:40,750
You're blushing.

782
00:40:40,910 --> 00:40:41,950
Are you feeling hot?

783
00:40:45,030 --> 00:40:45,750
Mind your manners.

784
00:40:48,830 --> 00:40:49,750
Wu Chen,

785
00:40:50,030 --> 00:40:51,880
on my master's orders, I have to go on a long journey

786
00:40:51,970 --> 00:40:53,400
and won't be back for several days.

787
00:40:53,860 --> 00:40:54,900
During that time,

788
00:40:55,080 --> 00:40:56,590
Xie Lingyun will come look after you.

789
00:40:56,830 --> 00:40:57,850
You stay here

790
00:40:58,010 --> 00:41:00,090
and practice the Ice Sword Technique that I taught you well.

791
00:41:00,170 --> 00:41:01,480
Remember, do not wander around.

792
00:41:01,710 --> 00:41:02,560
Can't I come with you?

793
00:41:02,580 --> 00:41:03,370
No.

794
00:41:07,190 --> 00:41:07,830
However...

795
00:41:08,280 --> 00:41:09,590
if you really have something urgent,

796
00:41:09,830 --> 00:41:11,190
use the Mind Stone to summon me.

797
00:41:11,520 --> 00:41:12,320
I will appear at any time.

798
00:41:12,340 --> 00:41:13,580
Mind Stone?

799
00:41:14,320 --> 00:41:15,710
You gave her the Mind Stone?

800
00:41:17,040 --> 00:41:17,950
He gave it to me.

801
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:18,710
Mo Xiao,

802
00:41:18,980 --> 00:41:20,540
you've really crossed the line this time!

803
00:41:20,810 --> 00:41:22,520
I've asked you for that stone for so many years,

804
00:41:22,550 --> 00:41:23,590
and you've never been willing to give it to me!

805
00:41:23,610 --> 00:41:24,550
And now what?

806
00:41:24,640 --> 00:41:26,560
You just handed it over to this girl you've barely known for five minutes?

807
00:41:29,630 --> 00:41:30,920
You must give me a

808
00:41:30,940 --> 00:41:32,120
reasonable explanation today.

809
00:41:32,300 --> 00:41:33,980
You, the dignified Young Master of the Tielyv Branch,

810
00:41:34,120 --> 00:41:34,880
have the Moye sword for protection,

811
00:41:34,910 --> 00:41:36,690
as well as so many mechanical gadgets up your sleeves.

812
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:38,040
Having my Mind Stone

813
00:41:38,060 --> 00:41:39,570
would just be adding another toy to your collection.

814
00:41:39,640 --> 00:41:41,430
Giving it to you would be a real waste.

815
00:41:44,330 --> 00:41:46,170
Whether I use it or not is my business.

816
00:41:46,310 --> 00:41:48,180
Whether you give it or not is your business.
